data.description: What you've been waiting for in Madison! 5 bedrooms, 4 baths, large lot, and great location in Madison School District. This home has new paint throughout out and is move in ready. This split plan features 4 bedrooms and 3 full baths downstairs and a 5th bedroom and bath upstairs which can also be used as a bonus room/office. The large kitchen has stainless appliances and plenty of space for gatherings.   The primary suite and bath have been updated and feature a large walk-in closet. All the bedrooms are spacious and beautiful wood floors throughout. The fenced in back yard is massive and has several areas for entertaining. Make your appointment today to see this great home.
